b'         Hello everyone,     Greetings from MITr!    Having a difficult time preparing for upcoming quizzes? Are you looking for a stress buster to ease you from all the accumulated pressure during the weekend? Need a small boost before you take on theremaining exams?      We understand that preparing for so many exams in a row can be quite stressful. To help you relieve the tension and sail through the quiz week with ease, we will be conducting aRelaxationsessionon 19 th March , Saturday from 10.30 AM  11.30 AM , in association with Medall. Theprogramwill be conducted in the  Aerobics Hall (   2nd Floor  , Sports Complex).   The session will focus onrelaxationexercises coupled with deep breathing and guided imagery. Theprogramis aimed to train you on skills to relax and manage stress more effectively.  Participation will be limited to 30 students for this session and hence it will be on a first come first serve basis.  If you are interested in attending thisrelaxationsession, please click here to register yourself.   All the best for your quizzes :)  Cheers, MITr team '

